{"tid":808723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英軍艦隻駛近西沙群島惹中方不滿，英國到港我帶路","createTime":"2018-09-06T14:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T00:52:23.000Z","uid":156652,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b80feeb0dd8de995886e1664e3a05726ca9d7285","tid":808723,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"英國皇家海軍兩棲攻擊艦海神之子號上周駛近南海西沙群島，中方批評是挑釁行為，已經提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息報道，海神之子號上周五前往越南途中駛近西沙群島，未有進入十二浬海里範圍，中方派出一艘護衛艦和兩架直升機，警告英方船艦離開，期間雙方保持克制。<br />\n<br />\n英國海軍強調，海神之子號是根據國際法行使自由航行權利。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部批評英方違反中國法律和國際法、侵犯中國主權，並提出嚴正交涉。"},{"pid":"2b82ab0c63f7aa904f07bafdf30a5a56c24cb78d","tid":808723,"uid":71768,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"如果 歐洲堅持咁行真係好易刷槍走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8ebd147b7450da0ff45caf756b3acc2005c4c0","tid":808723,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911fc3b2680e02947f9876cb420355a6ac9e36ff","tid":808723,"uid":135253,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線.... 英國到港仲洗你帶路？ 你方英女皇未撚來過呀？"},{"pid":"0da9a802693cc7fe4e50e9efab540095c7e710dc","tid":808723,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"你試下望出去睇下睇唔睇到大嶼山"},{"pid":"b22a8ab899f371a132f8172036fffce7164dc887","tid":808723,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"911fc3b2680e02947f9876cb420355a6ac9e36ff","tid":808723,"uid":135253,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線.... 英國到港仲洗你帶路？ 你方英女皇未撚來過呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyT